<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>验证码</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .verification-code {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 1px dashed #ccc;
    }
    .note {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .expire {
      color: #f44336;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>验证码</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>亲爱的 {{username}}，</p>
      <p>您的验证码如下，请在验证输入框中填写：</p>
      <div class="verification-code">{{code}}</div>
      <div class="note">
        <p>请注意：</p>
        <ul>
          <li>此验证码将在 <span class="expire">{{expiresIn}}</span> 后失效</li>
          <li>请勿将验证码分享给他人</li>
          <li>如果您没有请求此验证码，请忽略此邮件</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} CodeGeniusHub. 保留所有权利。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 